    {
        "content": "<p>and just to be sure: this feature adds the feedback logo to each section: <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/10155/j9x2sF1WVhbC9TAIohXQV3JE/image.png\">image.png</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/10155/j9x2sF1WVhbC9TAIohXQV3JE/image.png\" title=\"image.png\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/10155/j9x2sF1WVhbC9TAIohXQV3JE/image.png\"></a></div>",
