    {
        "content": "<p>the formurl (in the current implementation) is a google form to allow non-github users to create issues</p>",
        "id": 238662390,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1620931372
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>if you just want the footer, you can try this (this should not activate the feedback icons nor require the google form, but I haven't tested it):</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"YAML\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nt\">feedback</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"p p-Indicator\">-</span> <span class=\"nt\">active</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">dashboard</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">label</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">New Issue</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">url</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">https://github.com/cqframework/cqf/issues/new</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 238664372,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1620932357
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>and for added fun, you can add the link to the issues page as well as another feedback entry:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"YAML\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"nt\">feedback</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"p p-Indicator\">-</span> <span class=\"nt\">active</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">dashboard</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">label</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">New Issue</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">url</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">https://github.com/cqframework/cqf/issues/new</span>\n  <span class=\"p p-Indicator\">-</span> <span class=\"nt\">active</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"nt\">dashboard</span><span class=\"p\">:</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">label</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">Issues</span>\n      <span class=\"nt\">url</span><span class=\"p\">:</span> <span class=\"l l-Scalar l-Scalar-Plain\">https://github.com/cqframework/cqf/issues</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
        "id": 238664628,
        "sender_full_name": "Jose Costa Teixeira",
        "timestamp": 1620932443
